reviewText:
As usual everything went to plan.
There's not much more I can add.
So, once again thank you for your products and service.

I returned the DVD as it could not be played on any of my DVD players. It was formatted in country code 2 (Europe) and would not play on my US player (country code 1). Some DVD players can play anything but they are hard to find in the US. The seller returned my money.
